0871A46B.Toast: Vasily's Tree is weakening and needs help.

A5EFB09D.Phase26Description: I met a druid named Albard, the keeper of Vasily’s Tree. He says the tree is ill and needs a piece of the Great Oak, taken from the Underroot beneath Túr Dúlra. Who knows what I will find down there.

C9FCD1EA.Phase5Description: I went to the Underroot and took a cutting from the Great Oak. I should bring it to Keeper Albard and see if he can heal Vasily's Tree.
